        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You lob bombs unerringly, despite obstructions or distance.</p>\n<p>When you throw an alchemical item with the bomb trait, its range increment increases to 60 feet, you reduce any circumstance bonus to the target's AC from cover by 1, and you automatically succeed at the flat check when targeting a <a tabindex=\"0\" title=\"\" role=\"button\" data-trigger=\"focus\" data-toggle=\"popover\" data-boundary=\"window\" data-placement=\"auto\" data-html=\"true\" data-content=\"<p>While you are <em>concealed</em> from a creature, such as in a thick fog, you are difficult for that creature to see. You can still be observed, but you're tougher to target. A creature that you're <em>concealed</em> from must succeed at a DC 5 flat check when targeting you with an attack, spell, or other effect.</p>\n<p>Area effects aren't subject to this flat check. If the check fails, the attack, spell, or effect doesn't affect you.</p>\" data-original-title=\"<strong>condition: concealed</strong>\">concealed</a> creature.</p>"
